{"tid":2193532,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"終於發現左屙屎嘅奧義","createTime":"2020-09-08T02:35:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-08T13:37:24.000Z","uid":373220,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"321fde76ef1f733f765447a7997d9f54be61399c","tid":2193532,"uid":373220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T02:35:23.000Z","msg":"屙屎同做人一樣<br />\n唔可以強求<br />\n所以rule no.1屎必須要急先屙<br />\n亦因為唔可以夾硬嚟<br />\n所以2.屙屎唔可以谷住道氣咁谷屎<br />\n應該保持呼吸，然後用意念放鬆屎眼，當屎眼鬆開，啲屎就會好似流出嚟咁，順暢無痛<br />\n3.當一條屎完結，千萬不要夾埋屎眼，感受屎眼鬆開嘅感覺，有助唔使用力屙下一條屎<br />\n<br />\n只有做到以上三點<br />\n先至可以叫做識屙屎<br />\n否則好易有便秘同埋痔瘡<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e9011d079fa1470dc1fbc9feeac76d0d06d92d9","tid":2193532,"uid":251997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T03:51:13.000Z","msg":"我今日真係學到好多野<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b9888ee617a96a1bea53a668bfa2abab287f17a","tid":2193532,"uid":373220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4e9011d079fa1470dc1fbc9feeac76d0d06d92d9","tid":2193532,"uid":251997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T03:51:13.000Z","msg":"我今日真係學到好多野<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T06:32:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cac8fc39ff3c7a85e44f6d28bf70459004fa1ad3","tid":2193532,"uid":351202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T13:33:59.000Z","msg":"係唔係GAY PO黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0c5f9ffefe6affbb9af74d25f9fbeede7b03e73","tid":2193532,"uid":373220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cac8fc39ff3c7a85e44f6d28bf70459004fa1ad3","tid":2193532,"uid":351202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T13:33:59.000Z","msg":"係唔係GAY PO黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime"